title: Halo - Contact Harvest (audiobook)
description:
Contact Harvest is the fifth Halo book and it is presented here as a 10-cd audio book.

This is a prequel story which chronicles some early adventures of Sgt. Johnson and first contact with the Covenant.

I got tired of not seeing a torrent for this audiobook and broke down and bought it. I figured I&#039;d share it with everyone else as I&#039;m sure many of you have been waiting for this.

Enjoy!
